[article How to cut mosquitoes into sausages?
	[quickbook 1.7]
	[id how-cut-mosquitoes-sausages]
]

[role drop_menu
> [link mars-task Back: Mars Task][br]
]

This question is more like a richly imaginative imagination! In reality, mosquitoes are too small in size (usually less than 1 centimeter in length) and have a simple muscle structure, making them unable to be processed into sausages like meat. However, from a fun perspective, perhaps a creative sausage in the shape of a mosquito could be "replicated" using micro 3D printing technology?

